{
  "description": "A majestic landscape featuring a towering granite cliff face, likely El Capitan in Yosemite National Park, dominates the left side of the frame. The cliff is partially covered in vegetation, transitioning from green forests at its base to sparse shrubs and trees as it ascends. A deep valley stretches out below, filled with dense coniferous forest that extends into the distant background.  In the background, other mountain peaks are visible, with hints of snow on their upper reaches. The sky is overcast with layered grey and white clouds. The light is soft and diffused, creating a sense of grandeur and scale.",
